npc Smith 7 5 smith Well met! | Gruff but kind blacksmith who forges weapons and armor. Speaks plainly and directly. Proud of his craft. Will offer adventurers a sword if they learn about Amara's curse. Knows the Priest well — they grew up together. Distrusts magic but respects the Priest's faith. Knows directions: Princess Amara and the Priest are to the west (Old Chapel), the Tavern is to the east, and the Town Square, Forest Path, and old ruined Castle are to the south.
